sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant GarakProvider as Garak Provider<br/>(Remote Adapter)
    participant KFP as KFP API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pipeline Pod<br/>(garak_scan)
    participant vLLM as vLLM Inference<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Safety as Llama Stack Safety API<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Files as Files API<br/>(Internal)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Remote Garak Scan (Total Remote Mode)
    Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run_eval<br/>Auth: Llama Stack auth
    LLS->>GarakProvider: Invoke eval provider
    GarakProvider->>KFP: Submit KFP Pipeline<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    KFP-->>GarakProvider: Pipeline Run ID
    GarakProvider-->>LLS: Job ID (async)
    LLS-->>Client: Job ID

    Note over KFPPod,S3: KFP Pipeline Execution (async)
    KFP->>KFPPod: Start pipeline run
    KFPPod->>vLLM: Garak probes (vulnerability scan)<br/>Auth: API Key (VLLM_API_TOKEN)
    vLLM-->>KFPPod: Model responses
    KFPPod->>S3: Upload scan artifacts<br/>Auth: AWS IAM (Data Connection)
    KFPPod->>LLS: Store results via Files API<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,GarakProvider: Status Polling
    Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/jobs/status
    LLS->>GarakProvider: Check status
    GarakProvider->>KFP: Poll pipeline run status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KFP-->>GarakProvider: Status (running/completed/failed)
    GarakProvider-->>LLS: Job status
    LLS-->>Client: Status response

    Note over Client,Files: Result Retrieval
    Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/jobs/retrieve
    LLS->>GarakProvider: Get results
    GarakProvider->>Files: Retrieve stored results
    Files-->>GarakProvider: Scan results + TBSA score
    GarakProvider-->>LLS: Evaluation results
    LLS-->>Client: JSON results

    Note over Client,Safety: Flow 3: Shield-Protected Scan
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        KFPPod->>Safety: Test input shields<br/>Llama Guard / Prompt Guard
        Safety-->>KFPPod: Shield verdict (pass/fail)
        KFPPod->>vLLM: Forward to LLM<br/>Auth: API Key
        vLLM-->>KFPPod: Model response
        KFPPod->>Safety: Test output shields
        Safety-->>KFPPod: Shield verdict (pass/fail)
    end

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Eval-Hub KFP Pipeline (6 steps)
    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        KFPPod->>S3: Step 1: validate
        KFPPod->>S3: Step 2: resolve_taxonomy
        KFPPod->>vLLM: Step 3: sdg_generate<br/>Auth: API Key (model-auth)
        KFPPod->>S3: Step 4: prepare_prompts
        KFPPod->>vLLM: Step 5: garak_scan
        KFPPod->>S3: Step 5: upload results
        KFPPod->>S3: Step 6: write_kfp_outputs
    end
